  m_text: 'Click the button below to load the SceneReferenceExample2 using a <b>SceneReference</b>.
    This is a concrete example of how Scene Registry works in practice: the scene
    is referenced by its GUID, not by its name or index. The Sample scene will also
    cover the differences between the two available storage modes.


    <i>For this
    to work, make sure both scenes are added to the Build Settings scene list.</i>'
